    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Those who occupy or use land, buildings, or any other premises owned by another in consideration of some condition, typically the payment of rent.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
